cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.CL 

This paper deals with video data and deep learning, which are both commonly associated with computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. The use of neural networks also suggests that the paper could fall under machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the task of emotion recognition could be considered a human-computer interaction (cs.HC) or natural language processing (cs.CL) problem.
